text: As a given name, Toy may refer to: * Ah Toy (c. 1828–1928), Chinese-born American prostitute and madam * Toy Bolton, American 1960s NASCAR driver and team owner * Toy Caldwell (1947–1993), lead guitarist, main songwriter and a founding member of the 1970s Southern Rock group The Marshall Tucker Band ==See also== *Tó, nicknames *Ton (given name)
title: Toy (given name)
